| !Boot file for PlugPlay
| (C) Pace Micro Technologies plc 2000
|
| Last modified: 21-Apr-2000 (ADH)

Set      PlugPlay$Dir           <Obey$Dir>

| Plug-in support

Set      File$Type_BF8          MPEG
Set      Plugin$Type_BF8        PlugPlay
Set      Plugin$About_BF8       <PlugPlay$Dir>.About
SetMacro Alias$@PluginType_BF8  <PlugPlay$Dir>.!Run

| URI handler support

Set Alias$Open_URI_rtsp         <PlugPlay$Dir>.!Run
Set Alias$Open_URI_mpegv        <PlugPlay$Dir>.!Run
Set Alias$Open_URI_mpeg1ss      <PlugPlay$Dir>.!Run
Set Alias$Open_URI_mpeg2ts      <PlugPlay$Dir>.!Run

| Support the ANT URL protocol

SetMacro Alias$URLOpen_RTSP     Run <PlugPlay>.!Run -url %%*0
SetMacro Alias$URLOpen_MPEGV    Run <PlugPlay>.!Run -url %%*0
SetMacro Alias$URLOpen_MPEG1SS  Run <PlugPlay>.!Run -url %%*0
SetMacro Alias$URLOpen_MPEG2TS  Run <PlugPlay>.!Run -url %%*0

| Routine actions...

IconSprites <PlugPlay$Dir>.!Sprites
